Have Background allows you to display a random backround on every page. You can also set specific pages to show only a particular backup.

This is a work in progress and has not been tested 100%. Please send any bug reports to jonathan.finnegan@gmail.com

It includes "Color picker" by Author Stefan Petre www.eyecon.ro

http://jonathanfinnegan.com/have_background/
